title: DMC tape 1 images (February 1983) and the full set
description:
Pics of the very first DMC release from February 1983. I have uploaded the mixes from this first tape.
Tape??? Oh yes!!! Not many people know that this is how DMC started, before moving on to vinyl 18 months later.

And drool at the pic of all 17 tapes in the series, which ran until June 1984.
Watch out for mixes from some of these tapes coming soon.
